section 130. 
 
  (a) in sub-section (1), for the words “Notwithstanding anything 
contained in this Act, if ”, the word “Where” shall be substituted; 
 
 
 
(b) in sub-section (2), in the second proviso, for the words, 
brackets and figures “amount of penalty leviable under sub-section (1) 
of section 129”, the words “penalty equal to hundred per cent. of the 
tax payable on such goods” shall be substituted;  
 
 
 
(c) sub-section (3) shall be omitted. 
 
 
 
